the humblest object...

59:07.588 --> 59:08.759
into a totem...

59:09.524 --> 59:10.959
of great power.

59:15.062 --> 59:17.366
Now you keep this
close to your heart,

59:17.366 --> 59:19.297
and he cannot touch you.

59:24.275 --> 59:25.705
But lose it,

59:25.705 --> 59:28.075
or even worse,
throw it away...

59:38.852 --> 59:39.856
So, you keep ahold of it.

59:41.292 --> 59:42.089
No matter what.

59:47.960 --> 59:50.229
And now you're concerned...

59:51.304 --> 59:52.264
