Okay, babe, um...

01:01:10.182 --> 01:01:11.444
We'll see you tomorrow.

01:01:11.444 --> 01:01:12.511
<i>Yeah.</i>

01:01:12.511 --> 01:01:14.553
Yeah.

01:01:14.553 --> 01:01:19.018
