01:14:38.650 --> 01:14:39.986
Jake?

01:14:41.222 --> 01:14:42.021
Jake?

01:15:24.301 --> 01:15:26.703
Jake? Are you in here?

01:15:27.400 --> 01:15:28.540
Jake?

