01:24:58.037 --> 01:24:59.276
Pat. Pat!

01:24:59.276 --> 01:25:00.441
Pat!

01:25:02.348 --> 01:25:03.345
Pat!

01:25:04.009 --> 01:25:05.314
Pat!

