really wants you to know.

01:27:40.469 --> 01:27:42.306
Okay, so how much
do you love Fute, Jakie?

01:27:43.704 --> 01:27:46.277
Yeah. So a child's love
is a magical thing.

01:27:49.376 --> 01:27:50.380
Keep it close to your heart.

01:27:53.217 --> 01:27:54.318
